OL,3,CResidents flush loos with seawater on
OL,4,Cfifth day without mains supply
OL,6,FITV Meridian's Tony Green has spent
OL,7,Fthe day talking to customers and
OL,8,Fbusiness owners in Hastings
OL,10,FSeven thousand properties in East
OL,11,FSussex remain without water tonight -
OL,12,Fafter a mains pipe burst four days ago.
OL,14,FSouthern Water says two thousand of
OL,15,Fthose homes in St Leonards and
OL,16,FHastings are unlikely to have supplies
OL,17,Frestored until tomorrow.
OL,19,FAt its worst, more than in St
OL,20,FLeonards, Hastings and Westfield.
