OL,3,CResidents flush loos with seawater on
OL,4,Cfifth day without mains supply
OL,6,FThe disruption has had a major impact
OL,7,Fon businesses who rely on bank holiday
OL,8,Ftrade.
OL,10,FOne hotel owner says he's had to turn
OL,11,Faway half of his guests, and use sea
OL,12,Fwater to flush toilets.
OL,14,FAlthough the pipe was repaired on
OL,15,FSaturday, Southern Water had to
OL,16,Frecharge our network and restart their
OL,17,FBeauport supply works.
OL,19,FIn a statement on Monday afternoon
OL,20,Fthey said:
