OL,6,F"Around 25,500 properties in St
OL,7,FLeonards and Hastings have now had
OL,8,Fmains supply restored, though they may
OL,9,Fexperience reduced pressure for a time.
OL,11,F"Of the remaining 7,000 properties
OL,12,Faffected, a significant number are
OL,13,Fexpected to be back on supply later on
OL,14,FMonday.
OL,16,F"However, around 2,000 properties in
OL,17,Fparts of St Helen's and St Helen's
OL,18,FWood, which are normally served by the
OL,19,FFairlight reservoir, are unlikely to
OL,20,Fsee supply restored until tomorrow
OL,21,Fmorning or lunchtime.
