OL,3,CResidents flush loos with seawater on
OL,4,Cfifth day without mains supply
OL,6,F"This is because the reservoir is not
OL,7,Fyet sufficiently stocked to meet the
OL,8,Fdemand.
OL,10,F"Our bottled water stations will
OL,11,Fremain open each day from 8am-9pm and
OL,12,Fwe will continue to deliver bottled
OL,13,Fwater to customers on our Priority
OL,14,FServices Register until everyone is
OL,15,Fconfirmed back in supply.
OL,17,F"Efforts are underway to ensure
OL,18,Fsupplies to enable all primary and
OL,19,Fsecondary schools and colleges in the
OL,20,Farea to open as normal tomorrow."
