OL,4,Cfifth day without mains supply
OL,6,FThe company says that customers may
OL,7,Ffind their water is cloudy, which is
OL,8,Fcaused by air bubbles, or discoloured
OL,9,Fwhich is caused by iron deposits in
OL,10,Fthe pipes.
OL,12,FThey reassure customers that this is
OL,13,F"harmless" and can be remedied by
OL,14,Frunning the kitchen tap until the
OL,15,Fwater runs clear.
